  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nIn activity center, when u do have more than 1 mention and more than 1 reply, they are overlapping each other in the list\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n1. create a communty\r\n2. add some device u have access to (for example phone) to the community\r\n3. mention the user from desktop by the mobile device\r\n4. reply to some messages sent from desktop\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nMentions and replies are being shown in activity center as a list. User can click any record and be navigated accordingly\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1344\" alt=\"Screenshot 2021-11-19 at 14 50 48\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/82375995/142618738-faadad19-5e52-4510-98b4-3d88f3eaf31c.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1344\" alt=\"Screenshot 2021-11-19 at 14 49 48\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/82375995/142618759-a9d3f1a6-bd22-4ad5-9d55-4ee6ca6cd87c.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version: master from 19-nov-2021, commit `0597fab1ac57dc83872858ff30b99af8167d3210`\r\n- Operating System: macOS BigSur\r\n\r\n",
